        <hr/>
                        
<div class="txt-block" id="name-bio-text">
        <div class="name-trivia-bio-text">
                      <div class="inline" itemprop="description">
Jafar Panahi was born on July 11, 1960 in Mianeh, Iran. He is a director and editor, known for <a href="/title/tt1667905?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk1">In film nist</a> (2011), <a href="/title/tt0255094?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk2">Dayereh</a> (2000) and <a href="/title/tt0499537?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk3">Offside</a> (2006). He is married to Tahereh Saeedi.            <span class="see-more inline nobr-only">
                    <a href="/name/nm0070159/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bio_sm"
>See full bio</a> &raquo;
            </span>
</div>        </div>
</div>

                        
    <div id="name-born-info" class="txt-block">
        <h4 class="inline">Born:</h4> 
   
  <time datetime="1960-7-11" itemprop="birthDate">
<a href="/search/name?birth_monthday=7-11&refine=birth_monthday&ref_=nm_ov_bth_monthday"
>July 11</a>, 
     
<a href="/search/name?birth_year=1960&ref_=nm_ov_bth_year"
>1960</a>    
  </time>
            in
            <a href="/search/name?birth_place=Mianeh,+Iran&ref_=nm_ov_bth_place"
>Mianeh, Iran</a>
    </div>

                        
                        
